## 1. Project Environment
- Windows 11, Command line tool: PowerShell, commands separated by ';'

## 2. Project Structure 
- `/client` - React frontend code
- `/client/app` - Pages
- `/client/components` - Components
- `/client/hooks` - Hooks
- `/client/utils` - Utilities
- `/client/lib` - Libraries
- `/client/lib/apis` - API
- `/client/types` - Types
- `/client/public` - Public assets
- `/server` - Node backend code

## 3. Naming Conventions
- Component files: PascalCase (UserProfile.tsx)
- Utility files: camelCase (formatDate.ts)
- Variables: camelCase
- Constants: UPPER_SNAKE_CASE
- Components: PascalCase

## 4. Code Style
- Use 2 spaces for indentation
- Maximum line length: 100 characters
- React: Use function components and Hooks
- Node: Use async/await, RESTful API

